// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0050 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 968a4c77-52df-5c53-90ef-9b2fef2b2b9f

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:2* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
